      "content": "but isn't it true that some people argue wind isn't as \"green\" as it's made out to be because of the waste from the blades and the mining? it feels like the \"clean energy\" label is a bit of an oversimplification if the supply chain is that heavy. don't you think calling it \"clean\" is kind of misleading if you account for all that?",
